  <h2 class="heading-large">1. Vacancy summary</h2>
  <div class="grid grid-2-3">
    <div class="inner-block-padr">
      <div class="text">
        <p>This apprenticeship will have many different aspects to it including, learning to operate a variety of machinery and equipment to include Milling machines, Centre Lathes, Surface Grinders, Universal Grinder, Pillar Drills, Bandsaws, Bench Tools.</p>
        <p>The successful candidate will be required to manufacture parts using raw materials such as a variety of Steels, Brass, Bronze, Copper, Aluminium, Plastics and composites from Engineering drawings, sketches or verbal instructions.</p>
        <p>The successful candidate will also be:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Quality checking parts using appropriate measuring equipment. </li>
          <li>Recording process times. </li>
          <li>Reporting defects found. </li>
          <li>Plan process methods </li>
          <li>Ensuring work area is maintained to acceptable cleanliness level after use. </li>
          <li>Ensuring Health and Safety requirements are adhered to and where issues found reported immediately. </li>
        </ul>
